# Pre-built PhotonLibOS 0.8.4

This directory contains pre-built PhotonLibOS binaries for convenient and consistent deployment across different operating systems.

## Contents

- `photonlibos-0.8.4-linux-x86_64.tar.gz`: Pre-built binaries for x86_64 Linux systems
- `photonlibos-0.8.4-linux-aarch64.tar.gz`: Pre-built binaries for ARM64 (aarch64) Linux systems

## Future Plan

We intend to add support for building this dependency from source in a future release.
